{{External|rs=God pages}}
'''God pages''' (also known as '''torn pages''') are possible rewards from all tiers of [[Treasure Trails]] except [[Clue scroll (beginner)|beginner clue]]s. Each god page is coloured to represent their respective god: [[Armadyl]] is silver, [[Bandos]] is brown, [[Guthix]] is green, [[Saradomin]] is blue, [[Zamorak]] is red, and [[Zaros]] is purple. Four god pages, numbered 1 through 4, must be put in their respective [[damaged book]] to complete the [[god book]], however all four are not required at the same time to add pages to the book.

